because I don’t know why you say Jai.

00:43:14.640 --> 00:43:15.440
I don’t know why?

00:43:16.080 --> 00:43:16.800
What have I done?

00:43:17.880 --> 00:43:20.800
Why are you praising me I just don’t understand?

00:43:24.160 --> 00:43:26.160
If somebody says “Thank you very much Mother”.

00:43:26.720 --> 00:43:28.800
I don’t understand why they are thanking for what?

00:43:30.080 --> 00:43:30.880
What have I done?

00:43:32.720 --> 00:43:41.120
See this ego is the one that records\h
everything that this is what it is.

00:43:41.120 --> 00:43:44.560
I am such and I am such and\h
I am such, all falsehood.

00:43:46.080 --> 00:43:49.360
But if you don’t have such a record\h
in your head you cannot feel ego.

00:43:53.440 --> 00:43:58.960
If somebody says, “You are very good\h
looking”, immediately the balloon starts.

00:44:00.560 --> 00:44:01.360
Why is he saying?

00:44:01.920 --> 00:44:08.240
May be he wants some money, maybe he wants to use\h
you for some purpose, may be he’s praising because\h\h

00:44:08.800 --> 00:44:10.160
he knows you are a stupid fool.

00:44:13.280 --> 00:44:21.920
So why accept such a remark\h
as something great you know.

00:44:21.920 --> 00:44:25.760
And in this way we lose ourselves completely.

00:44:26.880 --> 00:44:29.040
Let us have a command of ourselves.

00:44:29.040 --> 00:44:30.000
Do we know ourselves?

00:44:31.360 --> 00:44:37.440
I know I am that, I know I am born like that,\h
I know all these things are there, so what?

00:44:39.920 --> 00:44:42.960
I mean I didn’t achieve\h
anything, you at least achieved.

00:44:43.520 --> 00:44:45.680
I never achieved anything; I was just like that.

00:44:48.240 --> 00:44:49.840
So, why to be conscious of it?

00:44:51.040 --> 00:44:53.760
That I am this, I am; I am nothing.

00:44:55.120 --> 00:44:56.640
Because whatever I am, I am.

00:44:58.160 --> 00:45:01.200
Now supposing this wood says\h
“Oh I am wood”, so what?

00:45:01.200 --> 00:45:04.320
You are wood after all.

00:45:04.320 --> 00:45:08.880
As simple as that, as simple as that.

00:45:10.560 --> 00:45:14.480
So, see this complications of\h
your mind should be reduced\h\h

00:45:14.480 --> 00:45:19.200
otherwise your attention will never improve\h
and what will happen is that you’ll not grow.

00:45:20.720 --> 00:45:21.840
And the dwarfs, you know?

00:45:23.120 --> 00:45:24.720
We’ll have all the dwarfs here.

00:45:27.200 --> 00:45:32.160
I want to show to Russians that\h
you are quite capable of growing\h\h

00:45:34.880 --> 00:45:39.760
and you are quite capable of\h
looking after your country.

00:45:41.600 --> 00:45:45.840
Your own President, his wife\h
all of them are funny people.

00:45:46.720 --> 00:45:51.440
Try to talk nonsense sometimes,\h
absolute, can’t understand.

00:45:52.640 --> 00:45:59.920
What business they have got to talk about other\h
countries when their own country is suffering so?

00:45:59.920 --> 00:46:05.200
There’s no introspection, there’s no understanding\h
what’s wrong with your own country and you start\h\h

00:46:05.200 --> 00:46:08.560
talking about other countries ‘this is\h
wrong with them that is wrong with them’.

00:46:11.760 --> 00:46:18.960
So in this atmosphere where you find a whole\h
lot of people have this problem of ego,\h\h

00:46:19.840 --> 00:46:24.320
you can only supercede them, only shine out,\h\h

00:46:24.320 --> 00:46:31.320
you can only save them by absolutely getting\h
rid of your ego, absolutely, hundred percent;\h\h

00:46:35.040 --> 00:46:35.920
in every way.

00:46:38.240 --> 00:46:40.160
You’ll see you’ll feel much lighter.

00:46:41.520 --> 00:46:44.880
Imagine you are hanging in the air, you\h
don’t know where you are going to land?

00:46:45.840 --> 00:46:46.880
How can you feel secured?

00:46:50.320 --> 00:46:52.560
As they say ‘stand on your legs’.

00:46:54.160 --> 00:46:56.640
It’s like that; stand on your leg.

00:47:01.360 --> 00:47:07.760
So now Sahaja Yoga is progressing very well,\h
very fast everywhere in the whole world.

00:47:09.200 --> 00:47:11.760
They gave Me a Doctorate, they did this,\h\h

00:47:11.760 --> 00:47:16.000
they are trying their level best\h
now to give Me a Nobel Prize also.

00:47:16.000 --> 00:47:20.240
Because only the Nobel Prize can put\h
these egoistical people all right.

00:47:21.440 --> 00:47:24.960
So they are working very\h
hard to get Me a Nobel Prize.

00:47:26.720 --> 00:47:31.360
All that is to show that people\h
will never accept me unless and\h\h

00:47:31.360 --> 00:47:33.680
until I have some sort of a brand on my head.

00:47:36.640 --> 00:47:43.600
But is important, in this world one\h
has to have some sort of a brand if he\h\h

00:47:43.600 --> 00:47:45.200
have to survive, everything.

00:47:46.880 --> 00:47:53.600
So, for you also it is important that you\h
have to have the brand of Sahaja Yogi.

00:47:55.200 --> 00:47:58.800
But in Sahaja Yoga if you have\h
the brand doesn’t work out.

00:48:00.400 --> 00:48:05.840
You have to have in reality\h
that power of Yoga within you.

00:48:07.120 --> 00:48:12.560
You can do a lot I know because you stand\h
on land of Shri Krishna and His power.

00:48:14.560 --> 00:48:20.320
Don’t need anything else, need;\h
don’t need any machinery, nothing.

00:48:20.320 --> 00:48:26.640
But only realize your responsibility, what\h
we are doing for Sahaja Yoga, for our self?

00:48:26.640 --> 00:48:27.680
How are we behaving?

00:48:28.800 --> 00:48:29.840
What is our style?

00:48:31.120 --> 00:48:33.920
How are we spreading Sahaja Yoga?

00:48:33.920 --> 00:48:34.560
Please try.

00:48:35.440 --> 00:48:39.120
If you can really introspect you’ll find\h\h

00:48:39.120 --> 00:48:44.960
that you’ll feel that we haven’t done much\h
for Sahaja Yoga that we could’ve done.

00:48:46.800 --> 00:48:50.160
Busy with yourself, with your own activities.

00:48:51.200 --> 00:48:54.080
But unless and until you do\h
for Sahaja Yoga something\h\h

00:48:54.880 --> 00:49:02.000
you have no meaning at all, you have no identity.

00:49:02.000 --> 00:49:09.840
If you can develop this beautiful\h
reflective nature by which you just\h\h

00:49:09.840 --> 00:49:17.120
reflect about yourself and not about others,\h
you’ll be amazed, how much will change.

00:49:18.640 --> 00:49:20.800
Even a simple meditation people don’t do.

00:49:21.680 --> 00:49:23.600
You get them an Ashram; there they fight.

00:49:24.800 --> 00:49:29.840
Do what you like ends up into something funny.

00:49:31.280 --> 00:49:36.640
I didn’t want to talk to you about\h
something unpleasant all the time.

00:49:36.640 --> 00:49:37.840
It’s not a very good idea.

00:49:38.560 --> 00:49:47.360
But I feel that you should now awaken to the\h
fact what is your responsibility as Americans?

00:49:48.720 --> 00:49:53.920
Very important, extremely important.

00:49:55.920 --> 00:50:02.480
And once you realize that you can do so\h
many things because you have got the Power.

00:50:03.200 --> 00:50:04.480
You have the Divine Power.

00:50:05.760 --> 00:50:12.560
But you must awaken and shed off this horrible\h
thing called ego, which makes you a monkey.

00:50:15.680 --> 00:50:19.680
I’ve seen this is the only problem you have.

00:50:19.680 --> 00:50:21.040
There’s not much conditioning.

00:50:21.920 --> 00:50:23.680
But this ego is the only problem.

00:50:23.680 --> 00:50:26.800
You don’t respect anyone, you\h
don’t respect this Motherland,\h\h

00:50:26.800 --> 00:50:29.600
you don’t respect even your self-realization.

00:50:31.040 --> 00:50:35.680
So this point today we have to know that we are,\h\h

00:50:35.680 --> 00:50:38.720
we cannot afford to have this\h
ego anymore on our heads.

00:50:39.760 --> 00:50:41.440
We just are not going to have it.

00:50:42.880 --> 00:50:49.600
We are going to humble down and we are going\h
to seek to things through our humility.

00:50:52.480 --> 00:50:59.600
Once you see these things work out\h
you’ll be the most important persons\h\h

00:51:01.760 --> 00:51:04.480
for even the Divine to deliver the goods.

00:51:06.560 --> 00:51:07.840
May God bless you.

00:51:08.400 --> 00:51:13.760
As it is we have now, I am awaiting\h
lots of Americans will become\h\h

00:51:15.600 --> 00:51:22.720
and what will convince them of you is\h
your humility and your good manners;\h\h

00:51:26.640 --> 00:51:27.440
very important.

00:51:30.080 --> 00:51:34.240
If these two things they\h
see in you they will change.

00:51:35.120 --> 00:51:36.480
I am sure they will change.

00:51:38.400 --> 00:51:43.360
Not to be aggressive with them.
